x@.@@@@.@x
.@@@@@@@.@
.@.@.@.@@@
x.@@@.@@@@
.@@@@@@@@.
x.x.@@@.x.
```

Consider your complete diagram of the paper roll locations. How many rolls of paper can be accessed by a forklift?

