.@.@@@@.x.
.x@@@@@@.x
.x.@.@.@@@
..@@@.@@@@
.x@@@@@@@.
....@@@...
```

(Continue removing rolls until no more are accessible...)

Stop once no more rolls of paper are accessible by a forklift. In this example, a total of 43 rolls of paper can be removed.

